Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.13,0:00:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我胸中的鼓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.17,0:00:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你延續而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.13,0:00:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.17,0:00:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使受了傷也無妨  不轉移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.17,0:00:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想熱切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.17,0:00:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我永不放棄的堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.17,0:00:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想緊緊抱著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.17,0:00:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.17,0:01:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.17,0:01:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引導至鮮明的、一瞬間的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.17,0:01:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我胸中的鼓勵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.17,0:01:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你延續而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.84,0:01:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和米利亞爾特大人你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.88,0:01:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想親眼看清楚戰爭是甚麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.68,0:01:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是最後一次戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.05,0:01:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零式讓我看了有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.89,0:01:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定和你們一起戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒傑克斯和特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這方法看來是最直接了當的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，帶桃樂絲小姐來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.87,0:01:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止米利亞爾特王兄的只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十三話\N[擊向地面的巨光]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後方有機體接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.79,0:02:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.93,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，如果是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們早就應該攻擊我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是萬年和平號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的穿梭機，請答話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.04,0:02:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然在那裡呢，諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉‧普奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來了強大的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能獲準降落嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛  五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧你們能沒被擊落來到這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時要你們關照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣，那不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們來到，我也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來會是一場痛苦的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥當然是痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那早就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我很軟弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.69,0:03:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我或許會很倚賴妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要倚賴的不是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.86,0:03:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子不再迷惘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到自己要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果得他們協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定會找到正確的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帶來麻煩的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這機體不是正常人能駕駛的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒叫你駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你駕駛過這東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能駕御它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝有相同系統的次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很有幫助吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部…\N傑克斯駕駛的機體嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟做過甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是正常人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，把維修班分成兩組啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙龍鋼彈的修理由我指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的…鋼彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦，你的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會馬上把它改為宇宙用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣機體變得能夠使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你也只會成為敵人的靶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不該回來戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖，乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦走了後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也很寂寞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次的表演…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,團長!這是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個衛星給OZ宇宙軍佔據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙要塞巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和月面基地的淪陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對OZ宇宙軍來說是致命的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.47,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直身為支配而君臨天下的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法從白色獠牙的追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.84,0:05:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和衛星居民的反感裡保護自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.17,0:05:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入完全孤立的狀態裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們OZ宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佔據了衛星C421
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要求你們歸還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.85,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們搶去的宇宙戰艦天秤座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們不答應這要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不保証衛星和居民的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的OZ也變得不擇手段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全因他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被白色獠牙迫到走投無路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ沒預先準備後路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會招致這情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.54,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倚賴MD的弱者們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始終只懂做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙會怎樣回應呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙也是由弱者組成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯不會答應OZ的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星的人會被見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫為了勝利的犧牲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這真的能稱為戰爭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何時候也卑鄙無恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能不管衛星居民的死活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可交出這艘艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，我們又肯定地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝勝利踏前一步了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米利亞爾特大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚…甚麼意思?桃樂絲小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們做出把居民捉為人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這等愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.48,0:07:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星的怒火應該會全部指向OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那豈不是見死不救…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把天秤座駛向衛星C421
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在改變方向的同時發射主砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知各有關人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米…米利亞爾特司令\N如果發射主砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.33,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只OZ，連衛星也會被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是戰爭啊，坎斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了勝利，我們要有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.51,0:08:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不惜任何犧牲的心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們的死會被寫成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了理想的可貴犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.65,0:08:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久遠地在衛星的歷史裡流傳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座改變方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前住OZ佔據了的衛星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是改變方向…嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算發射主砲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把衛星一起消滅嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.94,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾茵小姐妳想相信他的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的他是\N白色獠牙的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噴射器的調整待會才做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.84,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前，快點詳細檢查能量背包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，特洛瓦，甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，特洛瓦，你想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等!特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真胡來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對現在的特洛瓦來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛翼零式太危險了!  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真鎮定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微擔心一下同伴好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.73,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介入這場戰鬥是沒意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，哪吒一日未能動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零式能殲滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倚仗MD的OZ餘黨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果天秤座發射主砲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.21,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止那件事的不是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你靜待好消息，特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會搶回天秤座給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後把宇宙的霸權…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎?特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我稍微離開的期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ也變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後不准他們再自稱為OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我通知他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.64,0:11:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逐…逐出OZ?甚麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了特列斯大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯大人為何不承認我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把宇宙的霸權讓給白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了!是鋼彈!\N鋼彈出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要平安無事，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人排隊!別作聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.48,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防衛線看來被鋼彈衝破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望他們別再胡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是想過幸福的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該叫過你們住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說我們不會怕你們的裝腔作勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了…凱薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地照他們說話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,團…團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…這樣是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.66,0:13:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然以武力\N要所有人服從他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，他們是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道卻沒人想去糾正那錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們珍惜自己的性命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那傢伙不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦豁出自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想找出正確的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.47,0:13:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則，他應該不會做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.78,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時有危險的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?鋼彈為何會出現?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們和白色獠牙聯手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那即是說他們放棄衛星了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們所做的事的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要去救姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒來!特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.72,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有你一定要保護的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糾正我犯錯的人不是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.93,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的你要重覆犯那錯誤嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被0的系統迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該不是那麼軟弱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想保護的…人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.44,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦!特洛瓦!\N你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.41,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒錯，卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.42,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有…想保護的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦!你的…記憶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.33,0:16:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，凱薩琳在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?陶拉斯部隊\N全軍覆沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.98,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，只好拿居民作人質逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星內的陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加強外部閘門的戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚…甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.81,0:17:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈?甚麼時候…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，不被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潛入別人地方是我的專長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不準你們再傷害衛星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲，能量補充完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時能發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民間穿梭機\N從一點鐘方向接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄，我是莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了呢，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，一切已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.80,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄，我認為你是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不能阻礙天秤座的主砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只會白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使白死也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.95,0:18:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，讓我說幾句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.15,0:18:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然利用強大的武力支配別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自稱匹斯克拉福特不羞恥的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想說的只是那些話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲發射，開始倒數吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫白色獠牙的傢伙中止攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們所做的事是無意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座主砲的目標…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是那個衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?那麼…哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲，發射10秒前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你無論如何要攻擊衛星嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神不會饒恕這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄!請你醒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.04,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…很清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3，2，1，0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射偏了?是恐嚇嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座的目標是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於動手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.22,0:21:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們或許真的無能為力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.93,0:21:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信任你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.47,0:21:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該一定知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓這種悲慘的戰爭發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.67,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，請你們創造和平的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害!經過這次攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.09,0:21:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們會因為我們的力量而震驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲的測試非常成功呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是給特列斯的挑戰書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.50,0:21:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.50,0:21:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲的控制回路看來負荷過重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.67,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在處理中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.07,0:21:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點，敵人馬上會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.64,0:22:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵人?你的意思是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.31,0:22:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這宇宙裡最棘手最可怕的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.98,0:22:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.34,0:22:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.64,0:22:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.40,0:22:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.55,0:22:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.18,0:22:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.97,0:23:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.75,0:23:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.07,0:23:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.94,0:23:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.50,0:23:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應用次代系統的戰術程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開發成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝了那系統的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把迎擊的迪歐等人趕進危機裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛要求猶豫不決的卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.85,0:23:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕御零式系統擔任作戰指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.79,0:23:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對宇宙作出補償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第四十四話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.86,0:23:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈小隊出擊
